g linear on filling above 2/9. We\nargue that for filling near or larger than 2/9, the spectrum of the t-V AB$_2$\nchain can be viewed as a mix of the spectra of Luttinger liquids (LL) with\ndifferent fillings, boundary conditions, and LL velocities.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 10 Oct 2011 22:36:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 1 Jun 2012 12:44:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-04"}
